abo Esqueceu\"\n|-\n|  Matilde || Episode: \"Entre o C\u00e9u e a Terra\"\n|-\n| [[2003 in television|2003]] || Zuline || Episode: \"O Dia do Amor\" \n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[2004 in television|2004]] ||  ''[[Da Cor do Pecado]]'' || Mariana || Episodes: \"March 9\u2013April 23, 2004\"\n|-\n| ''S\u00edtio do Picapau Amarelo'' || Amorzinho || Episode: \"A Menina da Selva\"\n|-\n| [[2005 in television|2005]] || ''[[Alma G\u00eamea]]'' ||K\u00e1tia (Anja) ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\"| [[2006 in television|2006]] || ''Camilo em Sarilhos'' || Carminho || Episode: \"O Ponto\"\n|-\n| ''Sob Nova Dire\u00e7\u00e3o'' || Daniele || Episode: \"Madrinha S\u00f3 Tem Uma\"\n|-\n| ''Carga Pesada'' || Marcinha || Episode: \"Tri\u00e2ngulo das Bermudas\"\n|-\n| ''[[Cobras & Lagartos]]'' || Cac\u00e1 || Episodes: \"October 24\u201326, 2006\"\n|-\n| ''Papai Noel Existe'' || S\u00f4nia || Television special\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[2007 in television|2007]] || ''Eterna Magia'' || Matilde Sotero O'Neill || \n|-\n| ''[[Fa\u00e7a Sua Hist\u00f3ria]]'' || Ivonete || Episode: \"Pilot\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| [[2008 in television|2008]] || ''[[Casos e Acasos#15\u00ba epis\u00f3dio (\"A nova namorada, o chefe e o dia f\u00e9rtil\")|Casos e Acasos]]'' || Carol || Episode: \"A Nova Namorada, o Chefe e o Dia F\u00e9rtil\"\n|-\n| ''[[Toma L\u00e1, D\u00e1 C\u00e1]]'' || Vanessa || Episode: \"O Pecado Malha ao Lado\"\n|-\n| ''[[Casos e Acasos#33\u00ba epis\u00f3dio (\"A volta, a cena e as f\u00e9rias\")|Casos e Acasos]]'' || Ivete || Episode: \"A Volta, a Cena e as F\u00e9rias\"\n|-\n| [[2009 in television|2009]] || ''[[Caminho das \u00cdndias]]'' || Delegate Inoc\u00eancia || Episode: \"April 7, 2009\"\n|-\n| [[2010 in television|2010]] || ''[[Malha\u00e7\u00e3o]]'' || Marlene || Season 18; Special participation\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[2012 in television|2012]] || ''[[As Brasileiras]]'' || Astrid Meireles || Episode: \"A De Menor do Amazonas\"\n|-\n| ''[[Avenida Brasil (telenovela)|Avenida Brasil]]'' || Nicole || Episodes: \"September 28\u2013October 2, 2012\"\n|-\n| [[2013 in television|2013]] || ''[[Flor do Caribe]]'' || Doralice || <ref>[http://caras.uol.com.br/canal/nacionais/post/novela-sera-um-desafio-diz-rita-guedes-sobre-flor-do-caribe ''\u201cA novela ser\u00e1 um desafio\u201d, diz Rita Guedes sobre \u2018Flor do Caribe\u2019'']</ref>\n|-\n| [[2014 in television|2014]] || ''Quest\u00e3o de Fam\u00edlia'' || Neusa || Episode: \"N\u00e3o T\u00e3o Simples: Parte 1\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://revistaquem.globo.com/QUEM-News/noticia/2014/11/rita-guedes-aproveita-o-fim-de-tarde-para-se-exercitar-em-praia-do-rio.html|title=Rita Guedes aproveita o fim de tarde para se exercitar em praia do Rio|date=November 2, 2014|publisher=Quem|accessdate=December 4, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[2017 in television|2017]] || ''1 Contra Todos'' || Telma Dirceu || Season 2\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Film ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Year !! Title !! Role !! Note\n|-\n| [[1993 in film|1993]] || ''Tudo o Que Voc\u00ea Sempre Quis Saber Sobre o Amor'' || || rowspan=\"2\"| [[Short film]]\n|-\n| [[1998 in film|1998]] || ''O Maior'' || \n|-\n| [[2002 in film|2002]] || ''Separa\u00e7\u00f5es'' || Opening Night Guest || Uncredited\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[2003 in film|2003]] ||  ''Sintomas'' || || rowspan=\"3\"| [[Short film]]\n|-\n| ''Quem \u00c9?'' || \n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[2004 in film|2004]] || ''O Xadrez das Cores'' || Second employee\n|-\n| ''Procuradas'' || Angela ||\n|-\n| [[2005 in film|2005]] || ''O Farol de Santo Agostinho'' || Mother || [[Short film]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[2006 in film|2006]] || ''O Caso Morel'' || Carmem ||\n|-\n| ''Gat\u00e3o de Meia Idade'' || Eleonora, ex-girlfriend ||\n|-\n| [[2009 in film|2009]] || ''Fumando Espero'' || Herself || [[Documentary]]\n|-\n| [[2011 in film|2011]] || ''[[Qualquer Gato Vira-Lata]]'' || rowspan=\"2\"| \u00c2ngela || \n|-\n| [[2015 in film|2015]] || ''Qualquer Gato Vira-Lata 2'' || \n|-\n| [[2016 in film|2016]] || ''Mar Inquieto'' || Anita ||\n|